attachment. Overall, the results\npresented in this work show that the adoption of hydro-acoustically tuned\nresonant panels is a promising passive control technique for boundary layer\nseparation control.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 29 Jan 2017 20:55:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-31"}
