vely faint emission being\nseen near the outer edge and presumed forward shock. An animation is available.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 29 Jan 2017 22:43:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Mar 2017 11:27:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-19"}
