 theory of Schubert decomposition of\n$G/P$ for arbitrary splitting parabolic ind-subgroups $P\\subset G$, as well as\nthe orbits of real forms on $G/P$ for $G=\\mathrm{SL}_{\\infty}(\\mathbb{C})$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Jan 2017 04:21:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Jun 2017 19:10:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-07"}
