ically the order of\nmoments of the partition sum to the complex plane.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Jan 2017 14:14:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 May 2017 02:45:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-02"}
